      <title>卡尼在《每日秀》中表示，他准备以“局外人”的身份竞选加拿大总理</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/carney-tees-up-outsider-bid-to-lead-canada-on-the-daily-show</link>
      <description><![CDATA[前央行行长马克·卡尼在《每日秀》深夜脱口秀节目中几乎宣布将竞选接替贾斯汀·特鲁多并领导加拿大自由党。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/carney-tees-up-outsider-bid-to-lead-canada-on-the-daily-show</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 Jan 2025 12:38:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国标准官员即将对 Siddiq 展开调查并发布报告</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/uk-standards-official-probing-siddiq-is-set-to-report-shortly</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国首相基尔·斯塔默 (Keir Starmer) 的发言人周二表示，负责调查金融部长图利普·西迪克 (Tulip Siddiq) 财务状况的英国官员预计将“很快”提交报告，而首相面临越来越大的压力，要求她辞去金融部长的职务，因为该职务的职责还包括打击腐败。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/uk-standards-official-probing-siddiq-is-set-to-report-shortly</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 Jan 2025 12:33:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰连夜袭击俄罗斯能源和军事设施</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/ukraine-strikes-russian-energy-military-facilities-overnight</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰安全局官员称，大批乌克兰无人机夜间袭击了俄罗斯中部和伏尔加河地区的能源和军事设施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/ukraine-strikes-russian-energy-military-facilities-overnight</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 Jan 2025 12:25:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>赫格塞斯称他将成为五角大楼的“变革推动者”，在确认听证会上反驳批评者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/hegseth-says-he-d-be-pentagon-change-agent-rebuffing-his-critics</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当选总统唐纳德·特朗普选定的国防部长人选皮特·赫格塞斯将自己缺乏高层管理经验描述为一种优点，并在确认听证会的准备好的证词中表示，自己将成为一名“变革推动者”，“对某些公司、特定项目或已获批准的叙述没有既得利益”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/hegseth-says-he-d-be-pentagon-change-agent-rebuffing-his-critics</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 Jan 2025 12:22:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>希腊总理敦促欧盟加快解决能源价格过高问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/greek-premier-urges-eu-to-tackle-high-energy-prices-faster</link>
      <description><![CDATA[希腊总理基里亚科斯·米佐塔基斯呼吁欧盟考虑新的方法降低天然气和电力价格，作为提升欧盟竞争力的更广泛努力的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/greek-premier-urges-eu-to-tackle-high-energy-prices-faster</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 Jan 2025 12:16:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>电缆受损后北约将在波罗的海部署海军无人机</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/nato-to-deploy-naval-drones-in-baltic-sea-after-cable-damage</link>
      <description><![CDATA[北约将部署一支海军无人机舰队在波罗的海巡逻，加强对俄罗斯影子舰队海底电缆疑似破坏企图的应对。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/nato-to-deploy-naval-drones-in-baltic-sea-after-cable-damage</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 Jan 2025 12:10:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>波兰总统竞选竞争愈演愈烈，图斯克盟友地位下滑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/polish-presidential-contest-tightens-as-tusk-ally-loses-ground</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在距离选民投票还有五个月时，波兰总统竞选竞争愈加激烈，一位原本准备助推总理唐纳德·图斯克 (Donald Tusk) 议程的自由派候选人，却败给了一位得到反对派支持的民族主义历史学家。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/polish-presidential-contest-tightens-as-tusk-ally-loses-ground</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 Jan 2025 11:48:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>耶伦留下的联盟遗产被特朗普威胁摧毁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/yellen-leaves-legacy-of-alliances-that-trump-is-threatening-to-torch</link>
      <description><![CDATA[即将离任的财政部长曾试图在支离破碎的世界经济中加强联系，他警告说，当美国不单独行动时，它会更强大]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/yellen-leaves-legacy-of-alliances-that-trump-is-threatening-to-torch</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 Jan 2025 11:30:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德克萨斯州议员认为加州消防援助与条件挂钩</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/texas-lawmaker-sees-california-fire-aid-tied-to-policy-changes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着致命的山火继续在洛杉矶肆虐，来自德克萨斯州的一名共和党议员表示，联邦立法者将考虑将加州的救援资金与该州的政策变化挂钩。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/texas-lawmaker-sees-california-fire-aid-tied-to-policy-changes</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 22:20:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普和拜登称以色列和哈马斯即将达成加沙停火协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/sullivan-cites-distinct-possibility-of-gaza-deal-this-week</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普和乔·拜登都表示，他们乐观地认为以色列和哈马斯可以在几天内达成停火协议，从而暂停持续 15 个多月的加沙毁灭性战争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/sullivan-cites-distinct-possibility-of-gaza-deal-this-week</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 14:32:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
